title: Authorizes state residents to gather dead timber from the floor of the state forest preserve when such timber is on the side of a public highway
summary: Authorizes state residents to gather dead timber from the floor of the state forest preserve when such timber is on the side of a public highway.
actClause: Concurrent Resolution of the Senate and Assembly proposing an amendment to section 1 of article 14 of the constitution, in relation to the gathering of dead timber from the lands of the state forest preserve
